originalText.text: Outstanding urologist, one of the best in the USA. I have been his patient for more than a decade. He has operated on me twice with great success. I strongly recommend Dr. Te. He is a superb physician and oversees an excellent office and office staff.

text.text: Outstanding urologist, one of the best in the USA. I have been his patient for more than a decade. He has operated on me twice with great success. I strongly recommend Dr. Te. He is a superb physician and oversees an excellent office and office staff.

originalText.text: Doctor Te is an outstanding surgeon and practitioner. He did an amazing job managing my big urological problems that required medical knowledge, surgical skills, and interactions with other specialists. He was the best, He measured everything, if he wasn't looking at an image, he was evaluating a chart filled with data points or performing and exam. This is every time I see him. While his recommendations were well thought out and beneficial he only lacked on time and words. He talks little, he goes fast, but he does great! I've learn to trust him and have gain full faith in his doctoring. I  am a satisfied and grateful patient.

originalText.text: I found Dr. Te to be extraordinarily good: very experienced and having a great diagnostic approach and interpretation stemming from that. He communicates clearly and straightforwardly so one understands one's situation and the relative merits of the alternative paths forward. I highly recommend Dr. Te (as an individual who has experienced others in his field).
